headline: Altria Shares Surge 14% as Earnings Boost Drives Fresh Valuation Debate for 2025
summary: If you have been wondering what to do with your Altria Group shares, or thinking about jumping in, you are definitely not alone. Altria, ticker symbol MO, has been on the radar of both dividend lovers and value hunters, and for good reason. In the past month alone, the stock has surged almost 14%, adding to a hefty 40.5% return over the last year. headline: 2 Reasons to Like MO and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the past six months, Altria has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 16.2%. Its stock price has climbed to $67.75, representing a healthy 22.6% increase. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
